{"tid":1840174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港可能是下一個武漢 未來幾日可能是阻止病毒在香港擴散的最後機會","createTime":"2020-01-24T17:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T03:48:59.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f59cd9b238c871e0272415724b2b4990d36e81a","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎持續捇散，香港已經確診 5 宗個案，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何柏良晚上在 fb 發貼，指港大微生物學講座教授袁國勇的團隊在醫學期刊《刺針》發文，引述袁國勇指，武漢肺炎病毒的傳染性很高，香港、澳門以至其他國際城市很容易會演變成另一個武漢，或者 2003 年沙士期間的香港，未來幾日可能是阻止病毒在香港擴散的最後機會；在為時已晚之前，應呼籲全民戴口罩和經常用酒精搓手；何柏良更在貼文配上「新沙士」的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n何柏良除了貼出袁國勇團隊的文章，亦轉載一段袁國勇的訊息，指武漢肺炎的傳染性可以非常高，所以香港、澳門等地隨時有可能變成另一個武漢，甚至 2003 年的香港，由於病毒的潛伏期約 3 到 6 日，未來幾日可能是阻止來自大陸感染者，在香港傳播病毒的最後機會。<br />\n<br />\n但由於這些病人可能在來港時已經感染，但無發燒，令要發現他們非常困難，之後他們可能會透過分泌物傳播病毒，在醫院甚至居家傳播病毒；認為應該呼籲全民戴口罩，以及經常用酒精搓手，「before it is TOO LATE」，亦應該延長農歷新年假期直到情況穩定，以免返鄉的大陸學生將病毒帶回校園。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又指，有需要增加病毒測試設備、口罩和藥物存貨，用盡一切辦法延遲疫情爆發，直到氣溫回升，因為若溫度達 30 度，會減低武漢肺炎病毒存活。"},{"pid":"71684fc35efede4751c1f7748562b69c1fa52c2d","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:46:42.000Z","msg":"未來幾日可能是阻止來自大陸感染者，在香港傳播病毒的最後機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7d73b5d50075371a9ad955b58161cb49c3ba6b","tid":1840174,"uid":118888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"香港人口密度<br />\n世界第一<br />\n<br />\n盲都估到 再唔封殺中國人入境<br />\n難逃大爆發"},{"pid":"aacc5770fbc026252b1122d394e664d50828f151","tid":1840174,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封關 停課</span>"},{"pid":"fec1c4a293370848a871d5785e479ec9b0707ea1","tid":1840174,"uid":258830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:47:57.000Z","msg":"真係唔好等28號罷工&hellip;<br />\n支那陸續封城，就知有幾嚴重！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b6323b5fe37ce72ffd826b8b0172627b65950b","tid":1840174,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"初四五六<br />\n請到假既就唔好番啦"},{"pid":"414780a1520d83c3e3ef8c83e3cfab91caf8ccf3","tid":1840174,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"唔洗幾日就大撚鑊 一個星期都唔洗"},{"pid":"f464cce266bc1dbb435aeea64aac196528123488","tid":1840174,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5da14899191f6bf586e206281dd9e79ab2badc7b","tid":1840174,"uid":185925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd66dfb58bd864ad1fc4565fc73791be3b13eb59","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HoPakLeung/posts/10219187303806949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHoPakLeung%2Fposts%2F10219187303806949&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=479289a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HoPakLeung/posts/10219187303806949</a><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞"},{"pid":"8ce5c44fbf304726bbc78d527679f5d627a37938","tid":1840174,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我肯撚定政府想大爆發以控制逆權運動</span>"},{"pid":"2bff50a368ecc8d8b26e0fd99966452f159d3a4b","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"手足們 唔好死呀"},{"pid":"d130207509f870af62af59c3b839ca837c67fcda","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ae147bf0d8e53eee04b3a9e0ddb3b2910b8b2a3","tid":1840174,"uid":258830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce5c44fbf304726bbc78d527679f5d627a37938","tid":1840174,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我肯撚定政府想大爆發以控制逆權運動</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"根本無撚用，只會令更多人反政府！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608462ee9ba92fed13683fcd0ab8cd6d0f14741","tid":1840174,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=6f7f14ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9f277c3649f3bafe86f8d5692d4b2eb748b82245","tid":1840174,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工救港 功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5badbe370f397704f9bb6f0de57e25a84be3ab5f","tid":1840174,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c30d9cac41ca5e24bb477f40934a8bd3716897f","tid":1840174,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:57:16.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7e187257abe6fc77e3e490a9dec1531ad56bd6d5","tid":1840174,"uid":83914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚危急O既情況都要拖到初五先黎搞...<br />\n又打長期抗爭?"},{"pid":"927e1cc7147bb577b0e8cecf891e6c09991e581c","tid":1840174,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc83fc911821743d29b6602d7351d40dd0f22c7f","tid":1840174,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"？"}]}